<item>
            <title>[LU-15888] debian/control is being modified during build, causing builds to be flagged dirty</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15888</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;debian/control is being modified during build, causing builds to be flagged dirty&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let us follow the same pattern as debian/changelog -&amp;gt; debian/changelog.in&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So debian/control -&amp;gt; debian/control.in&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition libkeyutils1, libkeyutils-dev are needed during dkms builds on Debian (10) and Ubuntu (20.04) so add them to the lustre-client-* packages.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
